name: Tea Set
description: This little wooden tea set is perfect for play acting a meal with your dolls. This set has a pitcher, two cups and a serving bowl all hand painted with purple accents. (Non-toxic acrylic paint was used) The cotton drawstring storage bag is included.

name: Sweet Lovey
description: These little sweeties are sure to bring a smile to a child's face. The red babies are made from 100% up-cycled cashmere while the blue ones are crafted from a soft cotton velour. Both have organic cotton faces with hand-stitched features.

name: 12" Doll Outfit
description: Made from 100% cotton, this doll outfit is designed to fit any of my 12" dolls, even those made from kits. The clothes have no velcro that could snag on the yarn hair and no snaps or buttons to frustrate small fingers. Instead, they are intentionally simple to allow for easy hours for dress-up play!

name: 12" Waldorf - Inspired Doll - Vegan!
description:
Give the gifts of comfort and creativity with this sweet 12" doll. She comes as shown, with light organic cotton skin, brown organic cotton hair, and bright blue eyes. 
Unlike other Waldorf type dolls, she is completely made of natural plant fibers, so if you love the Waldorf style but want to avoid the wool, this little girl is for you! She is stuffed with kapok, which is a sustainable plant fiber harvested from the seed pods of the kapok tree.
